{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386100/extras/addtowishlist_gif.gif?t=1737210140\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>OVERVIEW</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Drift Survivors 2&quot; is the sequel to the acclaimed arcade game, now infused with roguelite elements. Upgrade your vehicle in intense battles and choose a gun that matches your style from random weapon drops! The online leaderboard is still there, challenging you to achieve higher scores in Endless Mode and make your mark!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GAMEPLAY:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1. Enjoy improved controls, allowing you to drift with ease and precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386100/extras/Gif_02.gif?t=1737210140\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2. While gamepads and keyboards capture the essence of action games, mouse input is also supported for a more accessible experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386100/extras/Gif_01.gif?t=1737210140\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3. Unlock a variety of vehicles and guns to create your perfect combat style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386100/extras/Gif_weapon_selected.gif?t=1737210140\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4. In Normal Mode, enhance your vehicle with attribute upgrade cards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3386100/extras/Gif_04.gif?t=1737210140\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p>